\'93Want me to take that off her?\'94 asked Harold Sr.\
It was a good question, though I didn\'92t like the answer.\
\'93Not yet.  Not until I\'92m sure she won\'92t cause a disturbance.\'94\
I moved to squat next to her so I could speak in a low voice.\
\'93Irene.  We know about the files in your case.  We know about the bomb.  I suspect this,\'94 I held up the tube, \'93is a remote detonator for the bomb, which I am almost certain is rigged to go off when we descend.\'94\
