\'93Fine,\'94 I said, sliding the gag back down to her mouth.  I leaned across her to grab the other side of her coat.  I ripped the seam open and pulled out as much nylon as I could.  \'93Pin her wrists in front of her so I can wrap up her arms.\'94\
